{"tid":119241,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"（重開）匯豐d複查煩過鬼","createTime":"2017-02-13T15:03:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T02:24:43.000Z","uid":84689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e75f4025cfb4d5763181fc1ed496bc9724664855","tid":119241,"uid":84689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T15:03:52.000Z","msg":"開咗吹水台太快沉重開 要比大家匯豐有幾垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我知佢地compliance department要跟規矩 但今時今日咁嘅服務真係唔得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一次打嚟問長問短 要人係電話度講好多資料查家宅 已經覺得唔妥當好唔安全 又問哂同呢個果個既錢銀來往 搵得錢少又話唔得<br />\n<br />\n第二次又話要寄份水電煤比佢做地址證明 寄咗去同佢確認哂無嘢要再交<br />\n<br />\n今日又話可能要交多份表格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我心諗 我間公司仔開戶口到宜家乜都無轉過 地址又無變<br />\n搵得果少少錢都話我洗黑錢！？<br />\n<br />\n講真 我覺得匯豐係借d意趕細客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我無比錢咩 煩左我幾個月仲成日send email嚟話未做完佢個複查要cut我account<br />\n比錢買氣受"},{"pid":"8126085c8e3cf406022b0680ecb9603328b3f7a7","tid":119241,"uid":84689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T15:04:25.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"807f064b206ecaa8b2614cc7fe0e1bcd70659d5c","tid":119241,"uid":29008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T02:05:19.000Z","msg":"過主囉，一定要用佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d76f211ab6768fc11b8873e400defdab71a75b","tid":119241,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T02:24:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}